    <Step id="aa2cc606-a252-408e-9b3c-e7fa0b3c0e6d" name="What Happens First?" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;We will:-&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='21'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Take the referral very seriously.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='21'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Listen to you.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='21'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Keep you informed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;When we receive a referral, we will make an immediate decision - is there immediate danger? If we think there is, we will take immediate action to safeguard with the persons agreement.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;If we think there is immediate danger and the person does not have capacity to understand the situation, we will take action that we consider to be in 'best interest' and which is the least restrictive option to safeguard the person.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;If we think that the person is NOT in immediate danger we will talk to or meet with other professionals to decide how to proceed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;We will identify someone to keep the person informed of what we are doing and why. This is likely to be a social worker.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
